      <title>阿达尼贿赂指控加剧魁北克养老金的印度噩梦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/adani-bribery-charges-add-to-quebec-pension-s-india-nightmare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的贿赂指控，使加拿大最大的公共养老金管理公司之一陷入困境，这加深了该公司因可再生能源投资失败而陷入的尴尬。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/adani-bribery-charges-add-to-quebec-pension-s-india-nightmare</guid>
